reviewText: I try to get all of the Veggie Tales that are out on the market.  The story lines are God's word on children's level.  I teach children, so I can use these sayings to help the children to understand God's word.
This is a DVD I would recommend for any one loves Veggies Tales.  I also recommend for children and any one else who wants some wholesome entertainment.
I bought this for my nephew and he really liked it. The packaging was not damaged and it was just like new.
